(8, 'Nest Ball', 'nest-ball', 33, 1000, null, null, 'Tries to catch a wild Pokémon. Success rate is 3.9× for level 1 Pokémon, and drops steadily to 1× at level 30.', 'Used in battle : Attempts to [catch]{mechanic:catch} a wild Pokémon. Has a catch rate of given by `(40 - level) / 10`, where `level` is the wild Pokémon''s level, to a maximum of 3.9× for level 1 Pokémon. If the wild Pokémon''s level is higher than 30, this ball has a catch rate of 1×. If used in a trainer battle, nothing happens and the ball is lost.'),
