(253, 'Zoom Lens', 'zoom-lens', 12, 4000, 10, null, 'Held: Provides a 1/5 (20%) boost in accuracy if the holder moves after the target.', 'Held: Raises the holder''s Accuracy by 20% when it goes last. Ingame description is incorrect.'),
