(255, 'Iron Ball', 'iron-ball', 15, 4000, 130, null, 'Held: Holder''s Speed is halved. Negates all Ground-type immunities, and makes Flying-types take neutral damage from Ground-type moves. Arena Trap. Spikes, and Toxic Spikes affect the holder.', 'Held: Decreases the holder''s Speed by 50%. If the holder is Flying or has Levitate, it takes regular damage from Ground attacks and is suspectible to Spikes and Toxic Spikes.'),
