(259, 'Icy Rock', 'icy-rock', 12, 4000, 40, null, 'Held: Hail by the holder lasts 8 rounds instead of 5.', 'Held: The holder''s Hail will create a hailstorm lasting for eight turns rather than five. As this item affects the move rather than the weather itself, the effect is not lost if the holder leaves battle or drops this item.'),
